ZH: 我们每个月都需要按时还款。
EN: We need to make repayment on time every month.

ZH: 每次忘记还款都会导致逾期费用。
EN: Forgetting to make repayment each time will result in late fees.

ZH: 这笔借款的还款期限是三年。
EN: The repayment term for this loan is three years.

ZH: 我们应该遵守合同中的还款条款。
EN: We should adhere to the repayment terms in the contract.

ZH: 还款的金额包括本金和利息。
EN: The repayment amount includes both the principal and interest.

ZH: 您可以选择每月固定还款额或灵活还款。
EN: You can choose between fixed monthly repayments or flexible repayment.

ZH: 这个月的还款截止日期是下周五。
EN: The repayment deadline for this month is next Friday.

ZH: 所有欠款必须在还款期内全额支付。
EN: All debts must be fully paid within the repayment period.

ZH: 如果无法按时还款，会出现财务问题。
EN: If unable to repay on time, financial issues will arise.

ZH: 每笔借款必须有明确的还款计划。
EN: Each loan must have a clear repayment plan.

ZH: 他们符合还款条件，因此获得了贷款。
EN: They meet the repayment conditions, thus they were granted the loan.

ZH: 请确保每笔交易都有记录以便追踪还款情况。
EN: Please ensure that each transaction is recorded for tracking repayment status.

ZH: 银行将按时收取每月的还款。
EN: The bank will collect monthly repayments on time.

ZH: 这项贷款的还款方式是每季度一次。
EN: The repayment method for this loan is once every quarter.

ZH: 如果缺乏资金，可能无法按时完成还款。
EN: If there is a lack of funds, it may not be possible to complete repayments on time.

ZH: 公司现在正努力筹集资金以实现还款目标。
EN: The company is now making efforts to raise funds to meet repayment goals.

ZH: 请提供最新的还款计划和财务状况。
EN: Please provide the latest repayment plan and financial status.

ZH: 每月的还款金额应尽量不超过收入的20%。
EN: The monthly repayment amount should not exceed 20% of the income.

ZH: 银行将根据您的信用记录决定还款期限。
EN: The bank will decide the repayment term based on your credit history.

ZH: 您必须在规定日期之前还款，以避免罚款。
EN: You must repay before the specified date to avoid fines.
